• I’ve watched censorship start to go crazy and watched Instagram and Facebook start this “Fact Checking” business a few months to combat conspiracy theories. My question is if “conspiracy theorists” are so blatantly wrong and the truth is so “obvious” why censor them? To me it only just proves we’re hitting a nerve. Good luck guys!! 👋🏻 We will find a way!!! ✊🏻✊🏻✊🏻
